column1: Baby Barnaby's////The first thing we liked was the free coffee outside while you waited. Although each container only held about 5 cups
column2: and ran out quickly. The food was excellent
column3: especially the very fresh squeezed orange juice. I ordered the corned beef hash with two fried eggs
column4: sunny side up. The food was excellent
column6: I kinda wanted some more corned beef. The fruit cup was fresh
